Achievements.Name: Very Lucky
Achievements.Description: Get 15 'Success' or 'Huge Success' chance cards in a single session.

Achievements.Name: Very Unlucky
Achievements.Description: Get 12 'Failure' or 'Huge Failure' chance cards in a single session.

Achievements.Name: Master Combatant
Achievements.Description: Complete 3 combats in a single run, without taking any damage.

Achievements.Name: Quick Reflexes
Achievements.Description: Reflect 100 projectiles over multiple play sessions.

Achievements.Name: Close Shave
Achievements.Description: Win a combat with less than 5 health remaining.

Achievements.Name: Very Brave or Very Stupid
Achievements.Description: Enter a combat with less than 5 health remaining.

Achievements.Name: Hunter
Achievements.Description: Land the killing blow on 10 enemies with a trap.

Achievements.Name: Slayer
Achievements.Description: Perform 2 prone attacks in a row.

Achievements.Name: Ninja
Achievements.Description: Kill an enemy with their own reflected projectile.

Achievements.Name: Master of Traps
Achievements.Description: Bash 5 enemies into traps in a single session.

Achievements.Name: Champion
Achievements.Description: Kill one of each monster type in a single session.

Achievements.Name: Well Equipped
Achievements.Description: Unlock every equipment card.

Achievements.Name: Well Travelled
Achievements.Description: Unlock every encounter card.

Achievements.Name: Dragon Slayer

Achievements.Name: King of the Undead

Achievements.Name: Arch Mage

Achievements.Name: Bling
Achievements.Description: Have 10 rings in your inventory at once.

Achievements.Name: Combat Ready

Achievements.Name: Release the Mages!

Achievements.Name: Release the Lich!

Achievements.Name: Release the Minotaur!

Achievements.Name: Wretched Soul
